web_snippets: With little known of the person's life and no record of her death, some have proposed that Jane Sharp is a pseudonym. ... Oxford Dictionary of National Biography.
A professor in the Department of Art History, at Rutgers University in New Jersey, USA, Jane Sharp also acts as Research Curator of the Dodge Collection.
Jane Sharp is the Director of the Certified Public Manager (CPM) Program in the School of Public Affairs and Administration (SPAA) at Rutgers University–Newark.
